---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="Steps">
  <section class="project-hero"><div class="hero-bg" style="background-image:url('/projects/steps/download.webp')"></div><div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container"><div class="hero-content"><a href="/#results" class="back-link"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M15 5L5 10L15 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Back</a><h1 class="project-title">Steps</h1><p class="project-tagline">Specialized pedicure brand</p><p class="project-context">Beauty / Wellness — USA</p></div></div>
  </section>
  <section class="project-section"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>01</i> Problem</span><p class="project-body">Getting to the right identity required deep analysis of psychological effects the brand needed to evoke. Steps offers professional pedicures with relaxing foot bath and aromatherapy. The identity needed to communicate calm, quality and professionalism simultaneously.</p></div></section>
  <section class="project-section-alt"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>02</i> System</span><p class="project-body">Clean, modern identity emphasizing typography and color. Created an inviting visual language matching clients' unspoken preferences for something feminine, classic and premium.</p></div></section>
  <section class="project-gallery"><div class="container">
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_prev.webp" alt="Steps"/>
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_2.webp" alt="Steps"/>
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_8841.webp" alt="Steps"/>
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_58.webp" alt="Steps"/>
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_71.webp" alt="Steps"/>
    <img src="/projects/steps/Branding-for-Beauty-industry_8271.webp" alt="Steps"/>
  </div></section>
  <section class="project-result"><div class="container"><div class="result-box"><h2>Result</h2><p>Approachable brand inspiring confidence and communicating relaxation. An identity clients associate with a quality experience before they walk in.</p></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>